//!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
//!                                                                            !
//! Dative verbs:                                                              !
//!   - Transitive (36DT)  [e.g., roubar, oferecer]                            !
//!   - Intransitive (33)  [e.g., agradar, telefonar]                          !
//!                                                                            !
//! Features used on these verbs:                                              !
//!   - Vdat:            The verb has a dative complement                      !
//!   - verbbeneficiary: The dative complement is the recipient of the object  !
//!                      or is the adressee                                    !
//!                      (o João ofereceu um livro [à Joana])                  !
//!                      (o João telefonou [à Joana])                          !
//!   - verbprivative:  The dative complement is the source of the object or   !
//!                      the victim/affected/patient                           !
//!                      (o João roubou um livro [à Joana])                    !
//!                                                                            !
//!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!

